Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:24.97,Ani,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\an6\blur0.5\fnTrebuchet MS\c&H01D0E7&\fscx135\fscy143\pos(1221,396)}в тени деревьев
